genresAdvancedInfo.name: psytech
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Psytech is a subgenre of techno music that incorporates elements of psychedelic trance. It is characterized by its fast tempo, pulsating basslines, and use of trippy and hypnotic sounds. The genre is often associated with underground rave culture and its use of complex rhythms and textures creates a frenzied and intense atmosphere.
